1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 6=

3
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,519
(Why?)

4
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:08,000
(His recent memories are all of me.)

5
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:12,400
(I need to go deeper into his mind.)

6
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:15,560
Young General,

7
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,280
we've caught him.

8
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:18,700
(Young Rong Xiu)

9
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:22,519
My father is the Grand General.

10
00:01:22,540 --> 00:01:24,820
(Young Feng Ye)

11
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,200
(Feng Ye's Father)
If you tell me where

12
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,439
(Feng Ye's Father)
your son is hiding,

13
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:29,640
I might spare your life.

14
00:01:30,239 --> 00:01:31,680
You'll never know.

15
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:50,200
(So Rong Xiu is the one
who killed his father.)

16
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:09,360
(This is)

17
00:02:09,719 --> 00:02:11,479
(the pendant he once asked me to find.)

18
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,400
(Father.)

19
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,520
(Rest assured.)

20
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:18,479
(I will use
the blood of the Rong family)

21
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:21,039
(to honor your spirits in heaven.)

22
00:02:26,719 --> 00:02:27,639
(My Lord,)

23
00:02:29,159 --> 00:02:30,800
(this bloodstained pendant)

24
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,719
(I have finally found.)

25
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,319
(Let's seal it with blood)

26
00:02:35,759 --> 00:02:37,680
(and walk this path
of revenge together.)

27
00:02:57,599 --> 00:02:58,360
(Yukui.)

28
00:02:59,719 --> 00:03:00,560
(Yukui.)

29
00:03:05,439 --> 00:03:06,560
(My Lord.)

30
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,280
(The pendant you asked me to find,)

31
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,960
(it's on the altar
in the mourning hall.)

32
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:13,120
(Even the deepest ripples
of your heart)

33
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,919
(are seen clearly
by these wounded eyes)

34
00:03:14,919 --> 00:03:16,680
(of mine.)

35
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,800
(Now is not the time for this.)

36
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:20,879
(Transfer the pain to me.)

37
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,280
(You go to the hall.)

38
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:25,719
(My Lord.)

39
00:03:26,439 --> 00:03:27,400
(When it comes to hatred,)

40
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:29,400
(you feel it more deeply than I do.)

41
00:03:30,159 --> 00:03:33,360
(Yet you repay others' wrongs
with kindness.)

42
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:36,520
(Those closest to you,)

43
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,879
(when others framed them,
why did you...)

44
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:39,719
(I must endure.)

45
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,800
(Endure until)

46
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,800
(the time is right.)

47
00:03:46,740 --> 00:03:49,900
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

48
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:54,080
(How can she be so calm?)

49
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,780
♪Trapped within the space
between your brows♪

50
00:03:55,780 --> 00:03:59,980
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

51
00:04:00,420 --> 00:04:03,580
♪The green lamp sheds no light
upon one who entered the path♪

52
00:04:04,060 --> 00:04:07,300
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

53
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:10,500
♪In dreams, it's you.
Beyond dreams, no one♪

54
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:13,820
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

55
00:04:13,820 --> 00:04:17,220
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

56
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:21,340
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

57
00:04:21,340 --> 00:04:24,500
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

58
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:27,900
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪

59
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,839
May Your Majesty

60
00:04:40,839 --> 00:04:42,399
enjoy robust health,

61
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:43,920
like the blessings in this dance,

62
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,439
years of peace

63
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,079
and lasting prosperity.

64
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:50,420
♪In dreams, it's you.
Beyond dreams, no one♪

65
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,519
Your Majesty.

66
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:52,480
Don't stop me.

67
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,160
Stand down.

68
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,800
Help me up.

69
00:04:57,420 --> 00:05:01,220
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

70
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:04,340
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

71
00:05:04,340 --> 00:05:07,860
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪

72
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,560
I knew

73
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,600
you would come.

74
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,000
(This is)

75
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:39,480
(the Palace of Punishment.)

76
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:51,480
(Your Majesty, please spare me!)

77
00:05:57,519 --> 00:05:59,040
(My Palace of Punishment,)

78
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,680
(do you like it?)

79
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,879
(Taste it again)

80
00:06:04,199 --> 00:06:06,480
(the sting of the whip.)

81
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,519
(How does it sound?)

82
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,519
(Your Majesty,)

83
00:06:14,519 --> 00:06:16,519
(I truly never plotted against you.)

84
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:18,240
(I beg you to investigate.)

85
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,199
(Sang,)

86
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,920
(which toy do you like best?)

87
00:06:36,439 --> 00:06:37,079
(Sang,)

88
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:39,319
(let's play another game.)

89
00:06:39,319 --> 00:06:40,800
(If you lose,)

90
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:43,000
(I'll cut a piece)

91
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:45,560
(of flesh from your body.)

92
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,480
(Deal?)

93
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,959
(Sister.)

94
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,000
Do you like it?

95
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,800
Every item in this room

96
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,920
was custom-made

97
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,879
by my orders,

98
00:07:12,879 --> 00:07:14,720
one of a kind in this world.

99
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:17,600
Every woman who comes here

100
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,079
is afraid

101
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:20,160
and terrified.

102
00:07:21,279 --> 00:07:22,800
It's as if

103
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,800
this place

104
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:26,040
is hell itself.

105
00:07:26,439 --> 00:07:27,959
And when that happens,

106
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,759
in my heart,

107
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,759
I feel an indescribable,

108
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,439
unspeakable

109
00:07:35,759 --> 00:07:37,519
pleasure.

110
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,279
Do you understand that feeling?

111
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:46,879
I want you to love

112
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,800
and hate

113
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,079
this place.

114
00:08:01,399 --> 00:08:02,160
My Lord,

115
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,879
are you alright?

116
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,040
How did the performance go?

117
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:05,959
Smoothly?

118
00:08:05,959 --> 00:08:06,600
Smoothly.

119
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:08,600
But it went too smoothly.

120
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:10,079
The Holy Maiden

121
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:11,920
was taken by the Emperor.

122
00:08:12,519 --> 00:08:14,040
How could this happen?

123
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:34,679
So

124
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:36,000
do you like it?

125
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,759
Yes.

126
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,159
They're afraid

127
00:08:41,519 --> 00:08:44,399
because they don't understand
the pleasure in it.

128
00:08:47,279 --> 00:08:48,600
That's an interesting

129
00:08:49,159 --> 00:08:50,720
way of thinking.

130
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,519
Do you know

131
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,360
that besides me,

132
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:59,399
there's one other person
who isn't afraid?

133
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,960
My elder sister,

134
00:09:02,519 --> 00:09:03,799
Jiang Yusang.

135
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,720
Your Majesty

136
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:09,320
must miss her dearly.

137
00:09:11,519 --> 00:09:12,960
You want to be her?

138
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:16,240
If my sister could do it,

139
00:09:16,799 --> 00:09:18,519
so can I.

140
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,600
Tell me more.

141
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,320
Compared to being forgotten,

142
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,679
isolated,

143
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:30,679
and abandoned,

144
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,759
what is physical pain?

145
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,759
I know

146
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:40,039
you want them dead.

147
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:50,000
My Lord.

148
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:50,759
You can't go in.

149
00:09:56,799 --> 00:09:57,320
My Lord.

150
00:10:02,519 --> 00:10:04,360
You never enter
the Palace of Punishment.

151
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,720
Why today?

152
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:06,440
Your Majesty,

153
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,559
we couldn't stop him.

154
00:10:07,559 --> 00:10:08,360
How dare you!

155
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,519
You dare stop him?

156
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:10,759
Get lost!

157
00:10:10,759 --> 00:10:11,360
Yes.

158
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:12,440
Go.

159
00:10:25,639 --> 00:10:26,960
You barged into the Palace of Punishment

160
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,519
for this woman.

161
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:29,440
It seems

162
00:10:29,799 --> 00:10:31,440
she holds a rather special

163
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,679
place in your heart.

164
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:34,799
You misunderstand, Your Majesty.

165
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:36,320
I was merely concerned for you.

166
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,159
My dear minister,

167
00:10:41,879 --> 00:10:43,120
what happened to your hands?

168
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,960
I left the hall in a hurry

169
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,600
and went to the Stargazing Pavilion
to divine for Your Majesty.

170
00:10:48,879 --> 00:10:49,399
Unfortunately,

171
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:51,320
I was cut by a nail
on the armillary sphere.

172
00:10:51,639 --> 00:10:53,279
My blood flowed into
the celestial markings.

173
00:10:53,759 --> 00:10:54,639
In fact,

174
00:10:54,639 --> 00:10:56,240
I was warding off calamity for you.

175
00:10:57,039 --> 00:10:58,480
(Young Prince.)

176
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,000
(As long as I'm in the harem,)

177
00:11:00,559 --> 00:11:02,559
(Young Zhu Yunqi)
(I will never let anyone)

178
00:11:02,559 --> 00:11:03,799
(bully you again.)

179
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,399
So I was

180
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:09,399
truly worried for your safety

181
00:11:09,399 --> 00:11:10,559
and came hastily.

182
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,240
Are you saying

183
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,759
she is a calamity?

184
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:19,200
This woman is not yet trained,

185
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:21,399
and she is a dark star
entering the palace.

186
00:11:21,919 --> 00:11:23,120
I fear

187
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,000
that if she stays too close to you,

188
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,759
it may shorten your lifespan.

189
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,679
I see.

190
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,200
Your divination arts

191
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:35,159
grow more mysterious by the day.

192
00:11:35,159 --> 00:11:36,799
Very well then.

193
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,840
Take her back.

194
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,200
I'm curious to see

195
00:11:40,559 --> 00:11:41,759
what kind of beauty

196
00:11:41,759 --> 00:11:43,519
you can shape her into.

197
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:44,799
Yes.

198
00:11:52,020 --> 00:11:58,020
(Nanfeng Pavilion)

199
00:11:58,679 --> 00:11:59,679
Let me go!

200
00:12:00,639 --> 00:12:02,039
Why did you stop me?

201
00:12:02,039 --> 00:12:03,919
Zhu Yunqi was convinced.

202
00:12:03,919 --> 00:12:05,360
If I had stayed tonight,

203
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,960
I could have followed the plan.

204
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,559
I could have taken revenge on him.

205
00:12:08,559 --> 00:12:10,600
You fell for Rong Zhaohua's trap.

206
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,600
She now knows

207
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:12,639
our entire plan.

208
00:12:12,639 --> 00:12:14,240
How do you know she knows?

209
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:15,080
And besides,

210
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,879
I can use the Divine Power
to control them.

211
00:12:16,879 --> 00:12:17,639
In that dungeon,

212
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:19,000
we suffered such severe wounds.

213
00:12:19,639 --> 00:12:20,399
Besides,

214
00:12:20,679 --> 00:12:22,200
the Emperor has a strong will.

215
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,399
In our current state,

216
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:24,399
we can't control him at all.

217
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:27,320
We won't know unless we try.

218
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:28,960
Hey.

219
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:35,919
My Lord!

220
00:12:53,940 --> 00:12:55,340
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

221
00:12:55,820 --> 00:12:57,260
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

222
00:12:57,460 --> 00:13:00,580
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

223
00:13:00,900 --> 00:13:04,700
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

224
00:13:07,660 --> 00:13:09,380
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

225
00:13:09,380 --> 00:13:10,900
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

226
00:13:11,260 --> 00:13:14,660
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

227
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:18,660
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

228
00:13:19,820 --> 00:13:22,980
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

229
00:13:22,980 --> 00:13:26,540
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

230
00:13:26,540 --> 00:13:28,860
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

231
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:33,060
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

232
00:13:33,500 --> 00:13:35,140
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

233
00:13:35,140 --> 00:13:36,660
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

234
00:13:36,660 --> 00:13:39,860
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

235
00:13:40,260 --> 00:13:42,180
♪In dreams, it's you♪

236
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:43,580
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

237
00:13:43,580 --> 00:13:46,900
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

238
00:13:46,900 --> 00:13:50,300
♪I can't forget the stars in your eyes♪

239
00:13:50,300 --> 00:13:53,860
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

240
00:13:53,860 --> 00:13:57,100
♪In this mortal world, there is only us♪

241
00:13:57,100 --> 00:14:00,540
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
